column5: Where are they available ? Are they worth the price or is it justeaiser to stay in a cabin ? Are they available on the east and west end of Lac Seul ? Thanks
Try www.lacseulfloatinglodges.com out of Hudson n ear the middle of the lake.
On the west side, the only one I know of is @ Whitewing resort by Ear Falls. Phone# 1-807-222-3000 1-800-265-1764
